!.env.*.example

# per-service env files (secrets) — <name>.env is the real file,
# <name>.env.example is the tracked reference. Infra services with no
# secrets (prod/services/redis.env, kafka.env, etc.) are tracked directly and
# NOT listed here — see prod/services/*.env.example for the full set.
prod/services/postgres.env
prod/services/rabbitmq.env
prod/services/mongo.env
prod/services/minio.env
prod/app.env
prod/nextjs.env

